prediction.sparql:
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q3577037 p:P161 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P161 ?actor .
  ?statement pq:P453 wd:Q3036775
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?place ?placeLabel WHERE {
  ?place wdt:P131 wd:Q16556 .
  ?place rdfs:label ?placeLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?placeLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?placeLabel ) , "park" ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?placeLabel ) , "museum" ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?placeLabel ) , "historical" ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?placeLabel ) , "building" ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?placeLabel ) , "attraction" ) )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?vicePresident ?vicePresidentLabel WHERE {
  ?vicePresident wdt:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?vicePresident wdt:P580 ?start .
  ?vicePresident wdt:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2001-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= '1993-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?vicePresident rdfs:label ?vicePresidentLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?vicePresidentLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?city ?cityLabel ?population WHERE {
  ?city wdt:P1082 ?population ; wdt:P17 wd:Q29 ; wdt:P31 wd:Q515 ; rdfs:label ?cityLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?cityLabel ) = 'en' )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?population )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?team ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 wdt:P54 ?team .
  FILTER ( ?team = wd:Q161337 ) .
  wd:Q169452 wdt:P2031 ?startDate
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?language ?label WHERE {
  wd:Q148 wdt:P37 ?language .
  ?language rdfs:label ?label .

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?superbowl ?year ?winner WHERE {
  ?superbowl wdt:P31 wd:Q32096 ; wdt:P585 ?year ; wdt:P1346 ?winner .
  ?winner rdfs:label ?winnerLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?winnerLabel ) , 'baltimore ravens' ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?case ?caseLabel WHERE {
  ?case wdt:P4884 wd:Q11201 .
  ?case rdfs:label ?caseLabel .

}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?vicePresident WHERE {
  wd:Q9640 wdt:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  wd:Q9640 wdt:P580 ?startTime .
  wd:Q9640 wdt:P582 ?endTime .
  FILTER ( ?startTime <= '1963-11-22' ^^ xsd:date && ?endTime >= '1961-01-20' ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?team WHERE {
  wd:Q296403 p:P54 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P54 ?team .

}

LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?primeMinister ?primeMinisterLabel ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q29 p:P6 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P6 ?primeMinister .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2011-12-31' ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= '2011-01-01' ^^ xsd:date ) OPTIONAL {
    ?primeMinister rdfs:label ?primeMinisterLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?primeMinisterLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?stadium ?city WHERE {
  wd:Q18708 wdt:P115 ?stadium .
  ?stadium wdt:P131 ?city .
  ?city wdt:P131 ?higherDivision .
  ?higherDivision rdfs:label ?cityLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?cityLabel ) = 'en' )
}
